'''小藍蟹'''（[[學名|學名]]''Callinectes similis''）是一種[[美青蟹屬|美青蟹屬]][[物種|物種]]。<ref name="Veracruz">{{cite journal en|journal=Crustaceana|volume=73|issue=3|pages=323–32|title=Observations on feeding, maturity and fecundity of ''Callinectes similis'' Williams, 1966, on the central continental shelf off Veracruz, Gulf of Mexico|author=Sergio Chazaro–Olvera, Arturo Rocha–Ramirez & Ramiro Roman–Contreras|doi=10.1163/156854000504417|url=http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/brill/cr/2000/00000073/00000003/art00007|year=2000|access-date=2010-06-21|archive-date=2011-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607044527/http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/brill/cr/2000/00000073/00000003/art00007|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==特徵==
小藍蟹最後的步足扁平，適合游泳。公蟹可以闊達12.2厘米，雌蟹則闊9.5厘米。<ref name="Puglisi">{{cite web|url=http://www.sms.si.edu/IRLSpec/Callinectes_similis.htm|publisher=Smithsonian Marine Station at Fort Pierce|title=''Callinectes similis''|author=Melany P. Puglisi|date=2008-10-01|accessdate=2010-06-21|archive-date=2010-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610120912/http://www.sms.si.edu/IRLSpec/Callinectes_similis.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

小藍蟹的最為接近''Callinectes danae''<ref>{{cite journal en|journal=Marine Biology|year=2007|volume=150|pages=1265–74|doi=10.1007/s00227-006-0437-7|title=Molecular phylogeny of the American ''Callinectes'' Stimpson, 1860 (Brachyura: Portunidae), based on two partial mitochondrial genes|author=Rafael Robles, Christoph D. Schubart, Jesús E. Conde, Carlos Carmona-Suárez, Fernando Alvarez, José L. Villalobos & Darryl L. Felder|url=http://www.springerlink.com/content/e66th102k51116x2/}}{{Dead link|date=2020年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>及''Callinectes ornatus''。''Callinectes danae''也在[[墨西哥灣|墨西哥灣]]出沒，更南至[[南里奧格蘭德州|南里奧格蘭德州]]；<ref>{{cite journal en|url=http://www.bioone.org/doi/full/10.1651/0278-0372(2001)021%5B0414%3ASASDOC%5D2.0.CO%3B2|journal=Journal of Crustacean Biology|year=2001|pages=414–25|title=Spatial and seasonal distribution of ''Callinectes danae'' (Decapoda, Portunidae) in Ubatuba Bay, São Paulo, Brazil|author=M. M. Chacur & M. L. Negreiros-Fransozo|volume=21|doi=10.1651/0278-0372(2001)021[0414:SASDOC]2.0.CO;2}}</ref>而''Callinectes ornatus''則分佈在[[北卡羅來納州|北卡羅來納州]]至南里奧格蘭德州。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sms.si.edu/IRLspec/Callinectes_ornatus.htm|publisher=Smithsonian Marine Station at Fort Pierce|title=''Callinectes ornatus''|author=Melany P. Puglisi|date=2008-08-01|accessdate=2010-06-21|archive-date=2010-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610132826/http://www.sms.si.edu/IRLSpec/Callinectes_ornatus.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>小藍蟹公蟹的第一及第二步足與''C. danae''及''C. ornatus''有所分別。<ref name="GSMFC">{{cite web|url=http://www.gsmfc.org/seamap/picture_guide/Crabs/callinectes.pdf|publisher=Gulf States Marine Fisheries Commission|title=Guide to Shelf Invertebrates, Gulf of Mexico|author=Perry and Larsen|year=2004|accessdate=2010-06-21|archive-date=2011-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110214140622/http://www.gsmfc.org/seamap/picture_guide/Crabs/callinectes.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>小藍蟹的甲殼上有6隻[[牙齒|牙齒]]，而[[藍蟹|藍蟹]]的只有兩隻。<ref name="GSMFC"/>

==分佈==
小藍蟹分佈在[[大西洋|大西洋]]、[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]及由[[美國|美國]]至[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]]的[[墨西哥灣|墨西哥灣]]。其北方界限位於[[德拉瓦灣|德拉瓦灣]]（Delaware Bay）。<ref name="Puglisi"/>在[[美青蟹屬|美青蟹屬]]中的[[物種|物種]]很易混淆，現時相信在墨西哥灣內（除了[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]）所有聲稱為''C. danae''及''C. ornatus''其實是小藍蟹。<ref name="GSMFC"/>

==生態==
小藍蟹棲息在[[沼澤|沼澤]]及[[河口|河口]]，在海灣中數量最多。它們只限於不少於15‰[[鹽度|鹽度]]的環境，而[[溫度|溫度]]也會影響[[繁殖|繁殖]]。<ref name="Puglisi"/>

小藍蟹主要吃[[植物|植物]]、[[魚類|魚類]]、[[多毛類|多毛類]]、其他[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]如[[北褐蝦|北褐蝦]]、[[軟體動物|軟體動物]]如[[侏儒蛤|侏儒蛤]]、及碎屑。<ref name="Veracruz"/>

小藍蟹會於[[春天|春天]]及[[冬天|冬天]]產卵，雌蟹會回到[[海濱帶|海濱帶]]產卵。<ref name="Puglisi"/>雌蟹平均可以帶著25萬顆卵。<ref name="Veracruz"/>

==漁業==
雖然小藍蟹並非主要漁獲，但有時也會與[[藍蟹|藍蟹]]一同被捕捉。<ref name="Puglisi"/>

